needed:
bluez,bluez-utils,pulseaudio,pulseaudio-bluetooth and a restart
start bluetooth:
sudo systemctl start bluetooth
add device:
$bluetoothctl
#power on
#devices/scan on
#pair Mac_adress
#trust Mac_adress
#connect Mac_adress
Switch audio profile so you can use mic:
pacmd list-cards
pacmd set-card-profile <index> handsfree_head_unit

